    "body" : "<h2><em>Box Drawing</em> characters in Unicode</h2>\n<p>Thanks to <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11827890/characters-for-ascii-print-of-table#comment15725588_11827890\">comment by valex</a>, the Unicode block <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Box_Drawing\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><em>Box Drawing</em></a> is indeed was I was looking for.</p>\n<p>Now my table is wonderful:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-none prettyprint-override\"><code>    ┌───────────┐\n    │  header   │\n    ├───┬───┬───┤\n    │ A │ B │ C │\n    ├───┴─┬─┴───┤\n    │ D   │ E   │\n    ├───┬─┴─┬───┤\n    │ A │ B │ C │\n    └───┴───┴───┘\n</code></pre>\n"
